Signing tool for PE-COFF binaries, hopefully at least vaguely compliant with
the PE and Authenticode specifications.

This is vaguely analogous to the tool described by
http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/8s9b9yaz%28v=vs.80%29.aspx

## Neverware

This fork contains a small hack to select the second certificate when
two certificates share the same nickname, this is a workaround for
https://github.com/rhboot/pesign/issues/45

The `neverware` branch contains our changes. After making updates,
make a new tag named `neverware-vNN`.
